                                    <span><p>A.  PayU inter alia has also entered into agreements with various Issuing Banks and other service providers for the purpose of providing equated monthly installment (EMI) payment plan scheme to the Customers holding credit cards and making payments of Customer Charge with respect to Products purchased on the Merchant Site.</p></span>
                                    <span><p>B.  The Merchant is further desirous of offering its Customers an option to make payments of Customer Charge using EMI facility offered by various banks through PayU.</p></span>
                                    <span><p>C.  PayU has agreed to provide solutions for processing EMI payment plan schemes of various Issuing Banks to the Merchant and the Merchant has agreed to avail the same on the terms and conditions hereinafter contained in this Agreement.</p></span>
                                    <span><p>D.  The Parties have further agreed to modify other terms and conditions of the Service Agreement as per the below mentioned term and conditions.</p></span>
                                    
